metadata.name: 9Bean #1
metadata.description: Unbeknownst to 9Cat at the time of its first encounter with 9Bean, it shares more than just friendship with the mysterious creature. 9Bean was formed in part due to 9Cat, with a little bit of magic, mystery, and good timing thrown into the mix. 9Bean will serve as a passive helper pet following right beside 9Cat wherever it goes, fighting baddies that try to hurt 9Cat.
